OL,3,CBlood scandal patient wants formal
OL,4,Capology from UK Government
OL,6,FA patient who received infected blood
OL,7,Fas a child is calling on the British
OL,8,FGovernment to formally apologise.
OL,10,FIan Walden from is one of an estimated
OL,11,F30,000 people treated with
OL,12,Fcontaminated blood across the British
OL,13,FIsles between 1970 and the early 1990s.
OL,15,FHe was given infected blood plasma
OL,16,Fboth on the island and in the United
OL,17,FKingdom.
