OL,6,F"I couldn't do sports, metalwork or
OL,7,Fanything considered dangerous."
OL,9,FIan took regular medication and had
OL,10,Fhours of blood plasma transfusions.
OL,12,FThen his treatment changed to a drug
OL,13,Fimported from the United States in the
OL,14,F1970s and 1980s known as 'Factor 8'
OL,15,Fwhich was infected with HIV and
OL,16,FHepatitis.
OL,18,FHe was diagnosed with Hepatitis C in
OL,19,F1994 and says the treatment for this
OL,20,Fcaused burning joints and hair loss.
