OL,6,F"We will continue to listen carefully
OL,7,Fto those infected and affected about
OL,8,Fhow we address this dreadful scandal."
OL,10,FGuernsey's Health President, Deputy Al
OL,11,FBrouard, explains they are aware of a
OL,12,F"small number, between five and ten
OL,13,Fpeople" who may be affected locally.
OL,15,FHe adds: "The UK Government is working
OL,16,Fon a compensation scheme and there is
OL,17,Fa Bill before the UK Parliament which
OL,18,Fnow covers this issue.
