OL,6,F"Currently, the focus of the Committee
OL,7,Fis working to ensure that affected
OL,8,Fpeople receive the support they need
OL,9,Fand any compensation that might be
OL,10,Fawarded to them by the UK Government
OL,11,Fin due course.
OL,13,F"Many people infected with bloodborne
OL,14,Fviruses (mainly Hepatitis C) through
OL,15,Fcontaminated blood or blood products
OL,16,Fhave been referred to the Orchard
OL,17,FCentre for treatment."
OL,19,FResults from a four-year UK inquiry
OL,20,Finto the infected blood scandal are
OL,21,Fexpected on Monday 20 May.
